195
00:11:06,620 --> 00:11:07,770
Chu.

196
00:11:08,830 --> 00:11:12,250
Wouldn't it be great

197
00:11:12,620 --> 00:11:14,220
if we weren't blood siblings?

198
00:11:17,540 --> 00:11:18,700
(What does he mean by that?)

199
00:11:18,900 --> 00:11:22,060
(Could it be that he found out
about my background long ago?)

200
00:11:27,380 --> 00:11:29,060
Zhen, you must be muddle-headed.

201
00:11:29,710 --> 00:11:31,700
How could you
say something that ridiculous?

202
00:11:34,590 --> 00:11:36,060
Chu, you're right.

203
00:11:38,740 --> 00:11:40,660
I was muddle-headed.

204
00:11:40,870 --> 00:11:43,060
How could I say something
as silly as such?

205
00:11:43,420 --> 00:11:45,520
Just take it as if
the conversation never took place.

206
00:11:59,710 --> 00:12:00,850
Chu.

207
00:12:01,780 --> 00:12:03,090
Take care.

208
00:12:08,619 --> 00:12:14,838
♪Fallen into rumors,
a sweet dream is disrupted♪

209
00:12:15,651 --> 00:12:21,856
♪I'm just a speck of dust,
stained with worldly attachments♪

210
00:12:23,055 --> 00:12:28,949
♪If illusion and reality go on
year after year♪

211
00:12:28,950 --> 00:12:34,743
♪My obsession is rekindled
by a dying kiss♪

212
00:12:36,902 --> 00:12:43,834
♪Though withered grass leaves no trace,
it buries a lifetime beneath♪

213
00:12:43,979 --> 00:12:50,881
♪Unsettled hatred
penetrates me deeper by another inch♪

214
00:12:51,404 --> 00:12:57,389
♪If deep affection
had never stirred my heart♪

215
00:12:57,390 --> 00:13:04,096
♪I would have missed the very person
as I turned back♪

216
00:13:04,350 --> 00:13:06,010
Loving without possession,

217
00:13:06,590 --> 00:13:08,640
